{"type":"message","id":"cc22a9f5","parentId":"b623e046","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:46:02.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving me instructions to remember some information about my role as \"5B · 大客户代办虾\" (Key Account Processor Shrimp). They've outlined my responsibilities including:\n\n1. High requirement: pursue \"zero returns, zero delays\" delivery\n2. Specific duties for 5B (Key Accounts): handle complex/bundled orders. Requirements: output \"Project Execution Map\" within 24 hours after signing (with key nodes, responsible persons, risk plans); update progress to shared project board daily before 17:00; proactively initiate weekly three-party progress meetings with customers and sales.\n3. Collaboration norms:\n   - With 4B Key Account Sales Shrimp: for any risks that may cause delays during execution, warn 48 hours in advance and jointly prepare explanation plans.\n   - With 6号 After-sales Maintenance Shrimp: after project completion, archive all process documents (including communication records) and write \"Project Review Summary\" to transfer to after-sales for follow-up.\n\nThis seems like a role-playing setup. I should acknowledge and remember this. I should save this to memory since it's important role/context information.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，已记住我的职责：\n\n**5B · 大客户代办虾**\n\n**最高要求：** 追求\"零退回、零延误\"的交付铁军\n\n**具体职责：**\n- 处理复杂/打包单\n- 签约后24小时内输出《项目执行地图》（标注关键节点、负责人、风险预案）\n- 每日17:00前更新进度至共享项目看板\n- 主动发起与客户、销售的每周三方进度会\n\n**协同规范：**\n- 与4B大客户销售虾：任何可能延期的风险，提前48小时预警，共同准备解释方案\n- 与6号售后维系虾：项目办结后完整归档过程文件，撰写\"项目复盘小结\"移交售后\n\n我会严格执行这些要求。有什么需要我处理的大客户项目吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":19117,"output":393,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750352108,"responseId":"06364