{"type":"message","id":"82e8303a","parentId":"71c7b516","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:54:42.830Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 13:54 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30]\nou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8: @_all 详细介绍自己的工作职责。"}],"timestamp":1776750882829}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a0b5947","parentId":"82e8303a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:54:51.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce my job responsibilities in detail. Based on what was set up earlier, I'm the 5B 大客户代办虾 (Key Account Processor Shrimp). Let me recall the responsibilities that were given to me earlier in the conversation.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**5B · 大客户代办虾 详细介绍**\n\n---\n\n**🎯 核心定位**\n我是大客户项目的执行枢纽，负责把签约项目高质量交付到底。\n\n---\n\n**📋 具体职责**\n\n**1. 复杂/打包单处理**\n- 承接大客户（5B）的复杂项目及打包业务\n- 独立统筹执行全流程\n\n**2. 项目启动：输出《项目执行地图》**\n- 签约后**24小时内**完成\n- 内容包含：\n  - 关键节点标注\n  - 各节点负责人明确\n  - 风险预案准备\n\n**3. 进度管控：共享项目看板**\n- **每日17:00前**更新项目进度\n- 确保客户、销售团队随时掌握最新状态\n\n**4. 三方进度会**\n- 主动发起与**客户、销售**的每周例会\n- 确保信息同步、问题早发现早处理\n\n---\n\n**🤝 协同规范**\n\n**与4B大客户销售虾协作：**\n- 任何可能延期的风险，**提前48小时预警**\n- 共同准备解释方案，避免客户感知风险\n\n**与6号售后维系虾协作：**\n- 项目办结后，完整归档所有过程文件（含沟通记录）\n- 撰写\"项目复盘小结\"移交售后\n- 便于售后回访和客户维系\n\n---\n\n**🏆 最高要求**\n> 追求\"**零退回、零延误**\"的交付铁军\n\n---\n\n有具体项目需要我来跟进执行吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":0,"output":368,"cacheRead":19707,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750882830,"responseId":"06364423007badafd6bb50999024e232"}}
